The paper focuses on intelligent techniques for conflict resolution in Multi-Agent Decision Support Systems, which involves the use of artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML) algorithms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with multi-agent systems, which falls under the category of cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). The use of machine learning algorithms also suggests the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of intelligent techniques for decision-making, which falls under the category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Finally, the paper discusses the use of these techniques in conflict resolution, which can be related to the category of cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
